imdb.plot outline: A lot of money is missing. Everyone is looking for her. Everyone wants her. But only one woman knows her secrets... The show follows SUNNY, a con artist, who reunites with her ex girlfriend/partner in crime, REIGN, for a series of short cons leading up to a long con with half a million dollars at steak. After a devastating breakup that leaves her M.I.A for 9 months, she finds herself right back in the addictive love affair with Reign and the fast lifestyle of a hustler!
imdb.title: Sunny Reign
plot: A con artist reunites with her ex-lover and partner in crime for a series of short cons that lead to a major con worth $150,00 dollars.::Anonymous
